description.p:
The invention further includes a method of acid etching a fracture face located in a subterranean production zone, which method comprises the steps of:
a) hydraulically fracturing a subterranean formation to produce a fractured formation having at least one fracture face;
b) injecting capsules containing a liquid acid into said fractured formation while maintaining hydraulic pressure on said fractured formation;
c) depositing said capsules in said fractured formation; and,
d) releasing said acid from said capsules thereby acid etching said fracture face.
